{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "6151e863780c3cb937f856bb", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": null, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": null, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "NTAS1", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76b2c52ffa3c944600df"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fec2b295b085ab6eb8d"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [{"title": "NTA Abhyas Paper", "value": "85", "isVisible": true}], "previousYearPapers": [], "question": {"text": "A large heavy box is sliding without friction down a smooth plane of inclination <math> <mtext>\u03b8</mtext> </math>. From a point&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">P</mi></math> on the bottom of the box, a particle is projected inside the box. The initial speed of the particle with respect to the box is&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>u</mi></math> and the direction of projection makes an angle <math> <mi>\u03b1</mi> </math> with the bottom as shown in the figure:<br />\r<br />\r<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/nta_abhyas/jee_main/images/WhatsApp_Image_2020-08-11_at_1.59.44_PM.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%; object-fit:contain\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 88px;\" /><br />\r<br />\rFind the distance along the bottom of the box between the point of projection&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">P</mi></math> and the point&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Q</mi></math> where the particle lands. [Assume that the particle does not hit any other surface of the box. Neglect air resistance]", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "9ix7V", "text": "<math> <mrow> <mfrac> <mrow> <msup> <mi>u</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup><mi>sin&nbsp;</mi><mn></mn><mn>2</mn><mi>&alpha;</mi> </mrow> <mi>g</mi> </mfrac> </mrow> </math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "6Lklr", "text": "<math> <mrow> <mfrac> <mrow><mi>u&nbsp;</mi><mi>sin&nbsp;</mi><mn></mn><mn>2</mn><mi>&alpha;</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mi>g&nbsp;</mi><mi>cos&nbsp;</mi><mi>&theta;</mi> </mrow> </mfrac> </mrow> </math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "Mb2lj", "text": "<math> <mrow> <mfrac> <mrow> <msup> <mi>u</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> <mi>sin&nbsp;</mi><mi>&alpha;</mi> </mrow> <mi>g</mi> </mfrac> </mrow> </math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "IP3Ax", "text": "<math> <mrow> <mfrac> <mrow> <msup> <mi>u</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup><mi>sin&nbsp;</mi><mn></mn><mn>2</mn><mi>\u03b1</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mi></mi><mi></mi><mi></mi><mi>g</mi><mi>cos</mi><mi>&nbsp;</mi><mi>\u03b8</mi> </mrow> </mfrac> </mrow> </math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/nta_abhyas/jee_main/images/41554511515.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%; object-fit:contain\" style=\"width: 220px; height: 141px;\" /><br /><br /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/nta_abhyas/jee_main/images/96564154.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%; object-fit:contain\" style=\"width: 200px; height: 252px;\" /><br />&nbsp;<div><p><i><span style=\"color:black\">u </span></i><span>is the relative velocity of the particle with respect to the box. Resolve <i>u</i>.<br /><span style=\"position:relative;top:0.0pt\">&nbsp;<math> <mrow> <msub> <mi>u</mi> <mi>x</mi> </msub> </mrow> </math> </span>&nbsp;is the relative velocity of the particle with respect to the box in <i>x</i>&nbsp;\u2013&nbsp;direction.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p><p><span style=\"position:relative;top:0.0pt\">&nbsp;<math> <mrow> <msub> <mi>u</mi> <mi>y</mi> </msub> </mrow> </math> </span><span>is the relative velocity of the particle with respect to the box in <i>y</i>&nbsp;\u2013&nbsp;direction.</span></p><p><span>Since there is no velocity of the box in the <i>y</i>&nbsp;\u2013&nbsp;direction, therefore this is the vertical velocity of the particle with respect to ground also.</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><i><span>Y</span></i><span style=\";\"> \u2013&nbsp;direction motion (Taking relative terms w.r.t. box)</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<math> <mrow> <msub> <mi>u</mi> <mi>y</mi> </msub> <mo>=</mo><mo>+</mo><mi></mi><mi></mi><mi>u</mi><mi>sin</mi><mi>\u03b1</mi> </mrow> </math> </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<math> <mrow> <msub> <mi>a</mi> <mi>y</mi> </msub> <mo>=</mo><mo></mo><mo></mo><mo>\u2212</mo><mi>g</mi><mi>cos</mi><mi>\u03b8</mi> </mrow> </math> </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<math> <mrow> <msub> <mi>S</mi> <mi>y</mi> </msub> <mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn> </mrow> </math> &nbsp;(activity is taken till the time the particle comes back to the box) </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<math> <mrow> <msub> <mi>t</mi> <mi>y</mi> </msub> <mo>=</mo><mi>t</mi> </mrow> </math> </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><span>Using, &nbsp;<math> <mrow> <mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mi></mi><mi></mi><mi>u</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac> <mn>1</mn> <mn>2</mn> </mfrac> <mi>a</mi><msup> <mi>t</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mrow> </math> we get\u2013</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"position:relative;top:0.0pt\">&nbsp;<math> <mtable columnalign=\"left\"> <mtr> <mtd> <mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mn>0</mn><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo> <mrow> <mi></mi><mi></mi><mi>u</mi><mi>sin</mi><mi>\u03b1</mi> </mrow> <mo>)</mo></mrow><mi></mi><mi></mi><mi>t</mi><mo>\u2212</mo><mfrac> <mn>1</mn> <mn>2</mn> </mfrac> <mi></mi><mi></mi><mi>g</mi><mi>cos</mi><mi>\u03b8</mi><mo>\u00d7</mo><msup> <mi>t</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mtd> </mtr> <mtr> <mtd> <mo>\u21d2</mo><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mi>o</mi><mi>r</mi><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mi>t</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac> <mrow> <mn></mn><mn></mn><mn>2</mn><mi>u</mi><mi>sin</mi><mi>\u03b1</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mi></mi><mi></mi><mi>g</mi><mi>cos</mi><mi>\u03b8</mi> </mrow> </mfrac> </mtd> </mtr> </mtable> </math> </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><i><span>X</span></i><span>-direction motion (Taking relative terms w.r.t. box)</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<math> <mtable columnalign=\"left\"> <mtr> <mtd> <msub> <mi>u</mi> <mi>x</mi> </msub> <mo>=</mo><mo>+</mo><mi></mi><mi></mi><mi>u</mi><mi>cos</mi><mi>\u03b1</mi> </mtd> </mtr> <mtr> <mtd> <msub> <mi>a</mi> <mi>x</mi> </msub> <mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn> </mtd> </mtr> </mtable> </math> </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><span>Again, using <math> <mrow> <mtext>\u2009</mtext><mi>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mi></mi><mi></mi><mi>u</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac> <mn>1</mn> <mn>2</mn> </mfrac> <mi>a</mi><msup> <mi>t</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> </mrow> </math> &nbsp;we get \u2013</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"position:relative;top:0.0pt\">&nbsp;<math> <mo>\u21d2</mo> </math> </span><span style=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<math> <mrow> <msub> <mi>S</mi> <mi>x</mi> </msub> <mo>=</mo><mi></mi><mi></mi><mi>u</mi><mi>cos</mi><mi>\u03b1</mi><mo>\u00d7</mo><mfrac> <mrow> <mn></mn><mn></mn><mn>2</mn><mi>u</mi><mi>sin</mi><mi>\u03b1</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mi></mi><mi></mi><mi>g</mi><mi>cos</mi><mi>\u03b8</mi> </mrow> </mfrac> <mo>=</mo><mfrac> <mrow> <msup> <mi>u</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msup> <mi></mi><mi></mi><mi>sin</mi><mn>2</mn><mi>\u03b1</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mi></mi><mi></mi><mi>g</mi><mi>cos</mi><mi>\u03b8</mi> </mrow> </mfrac> </mrow> </math> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<math> <mrow> <mrow><mo>[</mo> <mrow> <mo>\u2235</mo><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><mtext>\u2009</mtext><msub> <mi>t</mi> <mi>x</mi> </msub> <mo>=</mo><mfrac> <mrow> <mn></mn><mn></mn><mn>2</mn><mi>u</mi><mi>cos</mi><mi>\u03b1</mi> </mrow> <mrow> <mi></mi><mi></mi><mi>g</mi><mi>cos</mi><mi>\u03b8</mi> </mrow> </mfrac> </mrow> <mo>]</mo></mrow> </mrow> </math> </span></p></div>", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f", "66b79b34d4b564dfab4f94cc", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc11", "67fa5fef4468eb1307ceb0ad", "6807d2ad647479b8e8696479"], "cpyqbChapters": ["616023b19c52e0f28ddb0775", "616023b0de8166998bc42c6d", "616023af43c51275f749f558", "61964c73d9833a69946df6f2", "61e7bd6f3bf0edf6b5de3a0b", "61964c746f9d7c1ee88dadf2", "616023aeab028caf34f8696e", "61c089866e775b4063ccd8a4", "616023b0785fa46404399f50", "61bb820e7ded9395491665d7", "629109efb7e6d88372f6f913", "629f390d082fd4386414ddf1", "629f3a923db4e88dec15f6fb", "629621249a4459f8a4446124", "64eb06be3118f713ecfef063", "66d58535a75f